      • xmlToOpenTypes

        public static HashMap<String,OpenType<?>> xmlToOpenTypes(Reader input,
                                                         OpenMBeanInfoConversionUtils.IResolver resolver)
                                                  throws IOException,
                                                         org.jdom2.JDOMException,
                                                         OpenDataException
        Converts an XML document, read from the given character reader, to a map of open types.
        Parameters:
        input - the character reader from which to read XML data
        resolver - the OpenMBeanInfoConversionUtils.IResolver used to obtain a character reader for external XML document references encountered in this XML document
        Returns:
        the map of open type defined in this XML document, with keys corresponding to type definition names
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if input is null
        IOException - if an error occurs when reading XML data from the input stream
        org.jdom2.JDOMException - if an error is detected in the XML document
        OpenDataException - if an invalid open type definition is encountered

        Converts an XML document, read from the given character reader, to an open MBean info object.
        Parameters:
        input - the character reader from which to read XML data
        resolver - the OpenMBeanInfoConversionUtils.IResolver used to obtain a character reader for external XML document references encountered in this XML document
        Returns:
        the corresponding OpenMBeanInfo
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if input is null
        IOException - if an error occurs when reading XML data from the character reader
        org.jdom2.JDOMException - if an error is detected during the parsing or validation of the XML document
        OpenDataException - if an invalid open type definition is encountered

      • toOpenMBeanInfo

        public static OpenMBeanInfoSupport toOpenMBeanInfo(MBeanInfo mbeanInfo)
        Attempts to convert an MBean info into an open MBean info.
        The conversion will succeed only if the type of every attribute, constuctor parameter and operation parameter is equivalent to a simple type or to an array of simple types.
        Parameters:
        mbeanInfo - the MBean info to convert
        Returns:
        the corresponding OpenMBeanInfo, or null if mbeanInfo cannot be converted to an open MBean info
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if mbeanInfo is null
